# Cooking

Cooking transforms raw ingredients into nourishing meals. A skilled cook keeps settlements fed and morale high. Most recipes require a heating element or cooking station, and raw ingredients such as meats, produce, and grains.

## Cooking Equipment

A cooking stove or kitchen grill is needed for most hot meals. Place ingredients in the cooking device and wait for the recipe to complete.

